# Phase 0 — Why This Exists

## Historical Context

Legal professionals spend significant time on:

* Contract review
* Compliance verification
* Case law research
* Legal drafting
* Due diligence
* Risk assessment

Traditional workflow:

```text
Legal Document
      ↓
Lawyer Review
      ↓
Research
      ↓
Summary
      ↓
Decision
```

Problems:

* Thousands of pages
* Expensive legal review
* Slow research cycles
* Human bottlenecks

AI introduces:

```text
Legal Document
      ↓
AI Processing
      ↓
Clause Extraction
      ↓
Risk Detection
      ↓
Summary
      ↓
Lawyer Review
```

Lawyers focus on judgment rather than repetitive analysis.

